<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٤ - أخبرنا الْمَرُّوذِيُّ أَنَّ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ سُئِلَ عَنْ حَدِيثِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="c2">(صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ)</span> فِي الْحَسَنِ وَالْحُسَيْنِ <span class="c1">"أَنَّهُمَا سَيِّدَا شَبَابِ الْجَنَّةِ"</span>: أَصَحِيحٌ هُوَ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَإِنَّ قَوْمًا زَعَمُوا أَنَّهُ لَيْسَ بصحيحٍ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَأَنْكَرَ مَا قَالُوا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>